{"tid":996502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幸福國度的煩惱   比利時數萬學生為「全球暖化」罷課","createTime":"2019-01-26T10:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T11:19:03.000Z","uid":60281,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e6928360710d4a8f5f41748aba0d5f1ee3c34b0c","tid":996502,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/student_1JZGo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fstudent_1JZGo_1200x0.png&h=455e0271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比利時布魯塞爾有約 3.5 萬學生罷課，遊行往歐洲議會抗議，希望外界關注全球暖化及污染問題。有參與示威的高中生表示，「如果我們逢星期四罷課，全國甚至全世界都會看到這是一個問題。」<br />\n<br />\n當地不少學校對學生罷課寬鬆處理，部分學校只要求學生在遊行期間自拍，以證明他們缺席原因。<br />\n<br />\n示威由兩星期前開始，最初有3千人參與，上星期示威者增至 1.25 萬人。據當地警方指，本周四示威則是近年最大規模的學生示威。有學生高舉「尋求解決方法，不要繼續污染」(Be part of the solution, not the pollution) 的標語；有一名年僅 9 歲的女生則與老師一同參與遊行，並表示人們是時候以步行及單車取代駕駛私家車了。"},{"pid":"7a4e8df1a1b9bc5dc3bda2f96871cacabfc4b4f7","tid":996502,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AF%94%E5%88%A9%E6%99%82%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%A4%A7%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2-%E5%86%80%E4%B8%96%E4%BA%BA%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9A%96%E5%8C%96-%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%AF%AC%E9%AC%86%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E5%2586%2580%25E4%25B8%2596%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%25